results.titol: Pre-enrolment to official FIB Masters is now open 2025-2026

results.titol: Karina Gibert, professor at the FIB, will receive the Parliaments Gold Medal of Honor.
results.descripcio: The Parliament of Catalonia has agreed to award the Medal of Honor in the Gold Category to Karina Gibert, a professor at the FIB since 1990.
